        "Details": "Clan Jade Falcon's brand new super heavy mech design, this mech is heavily armed but with a somewhat eclectic hardpoint mount setup for a superheavy, with no ballistic hardpoints in the torso. Designed with heavy combat in mind, the mech has plenty of free tonnage to use for heavy weaponry. The primary layout mounts a pair of high powered Hyper Gauss Rifles for extreme damage, a pair of specialized plasma rifles designed for structural damage and a pair of unusual clan designed thunderbolt launchers.<br><br>S-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that substantially improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
